long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
YouCue is an unofficial plugin to cue another video to automatically play on YouTube.

Lets face it, sometimes you just want to listen to one of the suggested videos that appear in the side menu. When you're not signed in, at a party or just don't want to wait for the current video to stop playing, this handy little add-on will cue the selected video and start playing it when the current video is finished. 

Your next video is just one click away.
